 xander blakley quot a russian joke in his terrif book _siberia bound_ frenchman american and russian get to talk bout which countri has the more desir women frenchman say "ah when a frenchman put his hand around zee waist of his lover his finger form a complet circl and touch--not becaus his hand are so larg but becaus zee french woman waist is so slender." american say "yep but when an american woman get on a hors her heel reach all the way down to the ground--and it not becaus american hors are short but becaus american women have such endless long sexi legs." russian say "da but when a russian slap his wife ass on his way out of the hous in the morn it still jiggl when he come back after work--and it not becaus her ass is so big but becaus the russian work day is so short." tom URL